5% of its audience prefers mobile access. Regarding gender distribution, it caters to 59.87% male and 40.13% female users. The United States leads in usage, with Indonesia and the Philippines following. 惊人的 95% 的受众更喜欢移动访问。从性别分布来看，男性用户占59.87%，女性用户占40.13%。美国的使用量领先，印度尼西亚和菲律宾紧随其后。 The bounce rate of 60.38%, hovering slightly above the industry average, suggests areas for improvement. 60.38% 的跳出率略高于行业平均水平，表明有待改进的地方。 QuillBot 羽毛笔机器人 TViCbKfFDodEaDxjQBvc6wkBnWd.png  Although Quillbot had a dip in overall traffic, it recorded 1.1 billion visits between September 2022 and August 2023. 尽管 Quillbot 的整体流量有所下降，但在 2022 年 9 月至 2023 年 8 月期间的访问量达到了 11 亿次。 As a recognized figure in the AI Writing sector, users engage for an average of 20 minutes and 54 seconds per session, which is much higher than the industry average. 作为AI写作领域的公认人物，用户平均每次会话互动时长为20分54秒，远高于行业平均水平。 Desktop traffic leads with a significant 54%. Gender statistics indicate 59.85% male and 40.15% female users. 桌面流量领先，高达 54%。性别统计显示，男性用户占 59.85%，女性用户占 40.15%。 Interestingly, the Philippines leads in usage, with the United States and India trailing. The 75.20% bounce rate suggests potential areas for improvement in user experience. 有趣的是，菲律宾的使用率领先，美国和印度紧随其后。 75.20% 的跳出率表明用户体验有待改进的潜在领域。 Midjourney 中途 PlUzbvIELoZitbxqFX2cq4BunHf.png  Midjourney is the premier Image Generator, securing the fourth position on our list. Midjourney 是首屈一指的图像生成器，在我们的列表中排名第四。 This tool drove 500.4 million traffic between September 2022 and August 2023; users typically spend around 11 minutes and 43 seconds per visit (around the average).  2022 年 9 月至 2023 年 8 月期间，该工具带来了 5.004 亿次流量；用户每次访问的时间通常约为 11 分 43 秒（接近平均值）。 The platform sees a close traffic split between desktop and mobile users at 53% and 47%, respectively. A predominantly male user base, 92.19%, contrasts strongly with its female users at 7.81%. 该平台的桌面用户和移动用户之间的流量分布很接近，分别为 53% 和 47%。用户群以男性为主（92.19%），与女性用户（7.81%）形成鲜明对比。 The United States stands out as the primary traffic source, followed closely 