e period, with users spending an average of nearly 14 minutes per session.  人工智能写作工具NovelAI在此期间产生了2.387亿次访问，用户平均每次会话花费近14分钟。 The platform is accessed predominantly through desktops at 86%. The vast majority of its users are male, accounting for 91.67%. The US leads in traffic, followed by Japan and Indonesia.  该平台主要通过桌面访问（86%）。其用户绝大多数为男性，占比91.67%。美国的流量领先，其次是日本和印度尼西亚。 The bounce rate is 62.65%, suggesting a mix of user behaviors slightly above the industry average. Overall, NovelAI is a strong performer in both interest and usability metrics. 跳出率为 62.65%，表明用户行为组合略高于行业平均水平。总体而言，NovelAI 在兴趣和可用性指标方面都表现强劲。 CapCut 帽切 CapCut, the top video production AI tool, received 203.8 million visits between September 2022 and August 2023. 顶级视频制作人工智能工具 CapCut 在 2022 年 9 月至 2023 年 8 月期间获得了 2.038 亿次访问。 Users typically spend about 9 minutes and 45 seconds on the platform, which is below the industry average. More people accessed it via desktop (61%) than mobile (39%). Gender distribution was fairly balanced, with 53.95% male and 46.05% female users.   用户通常在平台上花费约 9 分 45 秒，低于行业平均水平。通过桌面访问的人数 (61%) 多于通过移动设备访问的人数 (39%)。性别分布相当均衡，男性用户占53.95%，女性用户占46.05%。 The bounce rate again leaves room for improvement as it’s slightly above the average. 跳出率再次留有改进的空间，因为它略高于平均水平。 JanitorAI 9.JanitorAI XOhybbmVTootibxoKnOcrQ3RnUb.png  JanitorAI, another AI chatbot tool, had 192.4 million visits from September 2022 to August 2023.  另一款人工智能聊天机器人工具 JanitorAI 从 2022 年 9 月到 2023 年 8 月的访问量为 1.924 亿次。 Users engaged with the platform for around 26 minutes and 53 seconds per visit, way above the industry average of 12 min 34s.  用户每次访问该平台的时间约为 26 分 53 秒，远高于 12 分 34 秒的行业平均水平。 Interestingly, a dominant majority accessed it via mobile (96%), with only 4% using desktop.  有趣的是，绝大多数人通过移动设备 (96%) 访问它，只有 4% 使用桌面设备。 The user base comprised 60% male and 40% female, a little more balanced than the industry average (69.5 to 30.5).  用户群由 60% 男性和 40% 女性组成，比行业平均水平（69.5 比 30.5）稍微平衡一些。 The US predominantly led in traffic, followed by Brazil, Malaysia, the Philippines, and Indonesia. The site had a bounce rate of 49.21%, which is solid compared to the industry average of 63.46%. 美国在流量方面占据主导地位，其次是巴西、马来西亚、菲律宾和印度尼西亚。该网站的跳出率为 49.21%，与 63.46% 的行业平均水平相比相当稳定。 Civitai 奇维泰 CyS5byrrko42SxxqsyScTK2enfh.png  Civitas, a top image generator tool, received 177.2 million visits between September 2022 and August 2023. 顶级图像生成工具 Civitas 在 2022 年 9 月至 2023 年 8 月期间获得了 1.772 亿次访问。 Interestingly, the average user stayed on the site for about 23 minutes and 19 seconds, almost double the industry average.  有趣的是，用户平均在网站上停留的时间约为 23 分 19 秒，几乎是行业平均水平的两倍。 Most users (58%) accessed the tool via mobile, while 42% used a desktop. 大多数用户 (58%) 通过移动设备访问该工具，而 42% 使用桌面设备。  Men comprised 88.79% of the user base, with women representing 11.21%. Regarding geographic distribution, the US had the highest traffic, followed by Japan, Indonesia, South Korea, and India. 男性用户占88.79%，女性占11.21%。从地域分布来看，美国的流量最高，其次是日本、印度尼西亚、韩国和印度。 The bounce rate was slightly under the industry average, so overall, Civitai impresses in usability metrics and could be used to understand better the interface users are looking for. 跳出率略低于行业平均水平，因此总体而言，Civita 在可用性指标方面给人留下了深刻的印象，可以用来更好地了解用户正在寻找的界面。  https://writerbuddy.ai/blog/ai-industry-analysis ',
